{"tid":1461183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分化撚收皮，走唔係問題，問題係你地會唔會返黎","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T07:20:23.000Z","uid":20231,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea7a13aac351f0cca3564b730ebc9049dc61153","tid":1461183,"uid":20231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"見好多分化撚屌人散水，想分化示威者。<br />\n根本一危險就應該走而唔無死頂，<br />\n你俾人拉左同殺左，就真係係得一次啦。<br />\n<br />\n根本有危險就走，見到安全返黎再佔過。<br />\n就可以做到一波又一波既攻勢。<br />\nBe water, 巨浪來襲前，水都會退得好快<br />\n<br />\n重點係：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">退既係人，唔係心中既火</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7dd2e3621c623d4010e2d3c3eb21d9422fb8bf","tid":1461183,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74b2a76180dda23cd592deccdc42ee6f5011ed96","tid":1461183,"uid":20231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c7dd2e3621c623d4010e2d3c3eb21d9422fb8bf","tid":1461183,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"門口同府邸隔咁遠，而且佢又可以住酒店"},{"pid":"4838917b45f614077e34cadc34b2f8a7d7a3a390","tid":1461183,"uid":306061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"我係分化撚，我係現場，散水撚翻黎未？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y66z5nv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy66z5nv.jpg&h=21c6d8e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f78597d43111a97294c5f23375ad945a98b0560","tid":1461183,"uid":20