:41:05.000Z","msg":"樓主係現場? 退唔退現場決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有人想衝就睇路<br />\n<br />\n和理非主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"係。<br />\n一直都現場決定，如果你地要堅持留守。<br />\n就算有幾多資料反對，都左右唔到你地。<br />\n但唔好再分化，叫散水係因為無人知港共會幾仆街。<br />\n琴日係有機會一次過推一班人去死"},{"pid":"9caab5a637835099ebd08226a5d926f0e88fea3e","tid":1461183,"uid":20231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"817aa0fb9642c00850e2a48fbbee4f5a1047bb9f","tid":1461183,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74b2a76180dda23cd592deccdc42ee6f5011ed96","tid":1461183,"uid":20231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c7dd2e3621c623d4010e2d3c3eb21d9422fb8bf","tid":1461183,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"門口同府邸隔咁遠，而且佢又可以住酒店"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"咁就破壞禮賓府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"破壞唔洗好多人，但好似破壞個制度既人都唔多"}]}